latestPosts.caption:
Save this reel if you’re tired of shopping at H&M and Zara!

I finally found a brand that gets the brief, cool embroidery, premium quality, and styles you can actually wear outside the house too. 😍

Just discovered @tigerthreadsatelier and I’m officially hooked. The fit is super comfy, the fabric’s breathable (Hello, Mumbai heat), and the vibe is so cool

I’ve styled these tees with everything- linen shorts, denims, cargos and they just work. Perfect for casual hangouts, brunch dates, or even a laid-back day at work.

So if you’re stuck in the loop of cliché fast fashion tees, here’s your sign to switch it up. TTA is more than just fashion, it’s a collectible T-shirt brand. Each drop feels unique, intentional, and designed to stand out.

(Ananya Bhonsle, t-shirts, embroidered t-shirts, embroidery, premium tees, loungewear, homegrown labels, Indian fashion, comfy t-shirt brands, how to style loungewear, fashion creator, explore, fyp)
